tally, significantly more than Trump&rsquo;s winning margin of roughly 11,000 votes in 2016.&quot;<br />\n&ldquo;The process ... will move forward,&rdquo; Whitmer said. &ldquo;Under Michigan law, the Board of State of Canvassers will now finish the job and I have every expectation they will certify the results when the job is done.&rdquo;<br />\n&quot;But this far-fetched scenario, which Trump allies have floated for weeks, ran into roadblocks just hours earlier.<br />\nMichigan Senate Majority Leader Mike Shirkey, a Republican, rejected the premise outright earlier in the day on Tuesday. He told Bridge Michigan &ldquo;that&rsquo;s not going to happen&rdquo; when asked about the possibility of the legislature selecting electors.<br />\n&ldquo;We are going to follow the law and follow the process,&rdquo; he said. &ldquo;I do believe there&rsquo;s reason to go slow and deliberate as we evaluate the allegations that have been raised.&rdquo;<br />\nThe state board of canvassers is scheduled to meet Wednesday afternoon.&quot;"},{"pid":"df4bbabc5ca26678bb7835c98419b930512d041b","tid":2290244,"uid":295230,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3f3781c8abe47c11baaa3ed7a3f69166b8571817","tid":2290244,"uid":283222,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T02:06:41.000Z","msg":"民主黨已有消息透露，即使聯邦高等法院最後栽决，特朗普先生勝，拜登總統在一月也會如期進註白宮，睬你岸九<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T02:08:43.000Z","msg":"有咩可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcadf837874d7077e7f358e954d885e7d1dc6e41","tid":2290244,"uid":35783,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"df4bbab